- I love this guy.

458
00:25:34,516 --> 00:25:36,084
- What's your name again?
- Verrall.

459
00:25:36,101 --> 00:25:38,102
- No, I mean your regular name.
- Paul.

460
00:25:38,103 --> 00:25:41,173
