a little time together.

488
00:27:22,332 --> 00:27:24,333
You and me, that is.

489
00:27:24,334 --> 00:27:26,732
- You don't say.
- Yes.

490
00:27:26,754 --> 00:27:30,298
- What are you, some kind of gigolo?
- Not exactly.

491
00:27:30,299 --> 00:27:32,300
