- Well, no.

521
00:29:01,890 --> 00:29:05,585
- Well, I'll tell you what I would like.
- Yes.

522
00:29:05,602 --> 00:29:09,332
- I'd like to learn how to talk good.
- All right.

523
00:29:09,356 --> 00:29:12,400
