too much slugging. I don't believe in it.

538
00:29:50,898 --> 00:29:54,343
- All right, I don't believe in it either.
- Good.

539
00:29:54,359 --> 00:29:57,588
- I learn pretty fast, don't I?
- You're great, Miss Dawn.

540
