549
00:30:25,557 --> 00:30:27,876
Oh.

550
00:30:30,312 --> 00:30:32,313
Let me ask you.

551
00:30:32,314 --> 00:30:35,816
Are you one of these talkers...

552
00:30:35,817 --> 00:30:39,237
