1575
01:39:37,205 --> 01:39:41,958
Sure. In this whole thing, I guess you
forgot about me... about how I'm a partner.

1576
01:39:41,959 --> 01:39:46,421
Jim once told me... 126
different yards I own.

1577
01:39:46,422 --> 01:39:49,299
- Control.
