1600
01:41:05,585 --> 01:41:07,586
Dumb chump.

1601
01:41:07,587 --> 01:41:09,588
Crazy broad.

1602
01:41:09,589 --> 01:41:13,049
To all the dumb chumps
and all the crazy broads...

1603
